name: RandomD4DJ
install_msg: Thanks for installing RandomD4DJ. Run `[p]help RandomD4DJ` to get a random D4DJ card from the Japanese version of the official D4DJ Groovy Mix game! If you need any help, feel free to join my server, at https://discord.gg/RSAetqdhRU and ask at the #noa-cogs channel.
description: Fetch an official D4DJ card, from the D4DJ Groovy Mix game.
end_user_data_statement: This cog does not persistently store any data about users
